部冇參與，即係德國內政<br />\n潛潛台詞：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b81843a1c33b917844b476053c55f7e2d68388c","tid":1174573,"uid":77196,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T03:02:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e588b6f6cd54ef48aedfcccfd93bdff132c0d1d","tid":1174573,"uid":137551,"like":74,"dislike":0,"score":74,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T03:02:41.000Z","msg":"依法審批<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18dd4dc8ac0b84fb6f04f2dadde1bba8f0dabf33","tid":1174573,"uid":41404,"like":194,"dislike":1,"score":193,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T03:03:21.000Z","msg":"德國駐港領事館今日（28日）發表聲明，指德國聯邦移民及難民部門所負責，並逐個個案根據其狀況作出決定，德國外交部並無權參與決定。德領事館重申，德國對港的政策以及與特區的關係仍然沒有改變。<br />\n<br />\n德國駐港總領事館就黃台仰以及李東昇獲庇護一事發聲明，指德國政府與香港仍保持良好的雙邊關係，德國對港的政策也仍然未變。就兩名港人獲政治庇護一事，由於資料需要保密為由，無法透露個別案件的內容。但聲明指，移民及難民部門是獨立決定尋求庇護人士的申請，並且是每個個案都是依法處理，而德國的外交部門在審理過程中是無權參與決定。德方最後表示，該國仍會與有關當局繼續了解事件。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190528/59649180\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190528%2F59649180&d=4a077UaaKOqSfaiyS2iiQTk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=fa2d5677\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190528%2F59649180&h=aa4ca98a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190528/59649180</a>"},{"pid":"30c39ff2d264c9f7fae8b455e6703235c1061a7a","tid":1174573,"uid":155095,"like":164,"dislike":0,"score":164,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T03:03:38.000Z","msg":"中國外交部無理指責德國外交部 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"